      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_7244565969886643072.png",
                "id": "talent8914",
                "key": "Lacerating Slash",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lacerating Slash"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>. The target character receives <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Total Collapse</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Total Collapse</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span> or <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> taken by the affected character increased by 2.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/bb0d49f020ec5da8ac945ca46a5f763f_5160903703918702879.png",
                "id": "talent48918",
                "key": "Tempestuous Barrage",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Tempestuous Barrage"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> and then separately performs \"<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Prepare Skill</span>\" for <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perpetual Cleansing</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate Cleansing</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Perpetual Cleansing</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span><br>(Prepare for 1 turn)<br>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> to the next opposing character on standby. After this, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Prepare Skill</span>: <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Ultimate Cleansing</span>. (If there are no opposing characters on standby, deals DMG to active character instead)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Ultimate Cleansing</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span><br>(Prepare for 1 turn)<br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> to the previous opposing character on standby. (If there are no opposing characters on standby, deals DMG to the active character instead)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/6d9f17ac20b8806cbca36313e77bdf23_659880963484043790.png",
                "id": "talent13891",
                "key": "Dvalin's Cleansing",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dvalin's Cleansing"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 5 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>. Applies <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Total Collapse</span> to all opposing standby characters.</p><p></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Total Collapse</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> or <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span> taken by the affected character increased by 2.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/fdffcf6a8e033feb0d73ad38a747e0e4_9043948330134805821.png",
                "id": "talent5815",
                "key": "Caelestinum Finale Termini",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Caelestinum Finale Termini"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Cryo DMG to all opposing chracters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl:</span> Deals 1 Hydro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Pyro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Electro DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_6804661944024124852.png",
                "id": "talent55087",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prepare Skill</span></strong></p><p>Some Skills cannot be used directly. Instead, they need to be <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span> over a certain number of turns.<br>When it is a certain player's turn, and this player's active character is currently <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill, this player's turn will be skipped. If the Skill has finished being <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span>, the character will directly use that Skill at this time. (Skills that require <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> cannot activate effects triggered by \"using a Skill\" or \"triggering an Elemental Reaction\" or other such effects.)<br>Only active characters can <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepare</span> Skills, and if an active character who is <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill gets switched off-field, their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparation</span> will be interrupted.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8513460012772825697.png",
                "id": "talent56432",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
